Privacy Policy

Last updated: 12.11.2024

1. Introduction
Welcome to ReddeR Taxi. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our app.

2. Information We Collect
We may collect the following types of information:

Personal Information: Information you provide to us directly, such as your name, email address, and phone number.
Usage Data: Information about how you use our app, such as the features you access and the time spent on the app.
3. How We Use Your Information
We use your information for the following purposes:

To provide and maintain our app.
To improve our app and develop new features.
To communicate with you, including sending updates and support messages.
To monitor the usage of our app.
4. Data Sharing and Disclosure
We do not sell or rent your personal information to third parties. We may share your information in the following situations:

With service providers who assist us in operating our app and providing services to you.
If required by law or to protect our rights and safety.
5. Data Security
We take reasonable measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure.

6. Your Rights
You may have the following rights regarding your personal information:

The right to access your information.
The right to request corrections to your information.
The right to request deletion of your information.
7. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy in our app. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.

8. Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:

Email: theredderteam@gmail.com
Website: https://redder.uz/
